data.description: *OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY, 1/28 FROM 2-4 PM!!  This beautiful and move in ready home is main level living at its finest!!  Open the front door to a large, open family room.  The home features a master suite with very large walk in closet with California Closet system and a spacious bath with garden tub and separate shower!  Enjoy the eat in kitchen with nice pantry/laundry room, also with California Closet system!  Open the doors from the lovely dining room to a patio in the fully fenced backyard.  New HVAC and front door!  You don't want to miss this one!!!
